data.description: Don't delay your chance to own this charming 4 bedroom cape cod in Sanders Subdivision.  Featuring 1st floor master with 2 spacious closets & full master bath.  Hardwood flooring throughout with gas fireplace to cozy up to in the winter.  Eat in kitchen with 1st floor laundry and half bath.  3 additional bedrooms upstairs with full bathroom.  Lots of storage.  Full basement.  Enjoy the secluded view of yard from your finished sunroom.  Roof & siding 4 yrs old.  Meticulously maintained.  Home Warranty, As Is
